{"word":"G1600 - ἐκπετάννυμι - ekpetánnymi - ek-pet-an'-noo-mee - Stretch forth","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκπετάννυμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekpetánnymi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-pet-an'-noo-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Stretch forth</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நீட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to spread out, stretch forth"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and a form of <a href=\"#/G4072 - πέτομαι - pétomai - pet'-om-ahee/4072\">G4072</a>; to <i>fly out</i>, that is, (by analogy) <i>extend:</i> - stretch forth.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}